# Mosquitto Access Control List (ACL)
# NFT Greenhouse Management System

# User greenhouse (IoT devices) can publish to sensor topics
user greenhouse
topic write greenhouse/+/sensor
topic write greenhouse/+/status
topic read greenhouse/commands/#

# User backend (server) can read all sensor topics and write commands
user backend
topic read greenhouse/+/sensor
topic read greenhouse/+/status
topic write greenhouse/commands/#

# Pattern for all greenhouse topics
pattern read greenhouse/#
